export const months = [
    'January',
    'February',
    'March',
    'April',
    'May',
    'June',
    'July',
    'August',
    'September',
    'October',
    'November',
    'December'
]

export const getRandomMonth = () => {
    return months[Math.floor(Math.random() * months.length)]
}
